abstract: Stephen Holden reviews performance by singer Paulo Szot at 54 Below.
lead_paragraph: Mr. Szot used his powerful baritone in songs by Antônio Carlos Jobim and Irving Berlin during his tribute to Frank Sinatra.

headline.main: Review: Paulo Szot’s Commanding Take on Bossa Nova at 54 Below
